text: Justine Gail Tinio (born December 3, 1995) is a Filipina foil fencer. She is an Individual Foil Silver Medalist as well as a member of the Team Foil that won a Bronze Medal at the 2015 Southeast Asian Games. Tinio is also the champion at the women's individual foil at the 2014 Philippine National Games. Tinio is currently a college student at the University of the East as of June 2015. As a representative of her college she is also named MVP for women's fencing at the Fencing championship of UAAP Season 77. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Filipino female fencers Category:University Athletic Association of the Philippines players Category:Southeast Asian Games medalists in fencing Category:Southeast Asian Games silver medalists for the Philippines Category:Southeast Asian Games bronze medalists for the Philippines Category:Fencers at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Competitors at the 2015 Southeast Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for the Philippines Category:Competitors at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games
